_sText:
Never ending wilderness might have an escape...
===============================================

A chill and pretty easy autobunnyhop map. Quite short (2-5 minutes). Can be beaten legit/400vel but whether it's enjoyable is another thing.
_Can you find all the hidden marks?_ ;)

- **Anti-aliasing might cause weird white lines. You have been warned.**
- Fps drops? Don't like how the map looks? **r_3dsky 0** is your friend!
- The underground part is not there to annoy you with 64-unit jumps. In fact, you can beat it without ever doing them. Perhaps your route needs to be changed... Who knows, maybe it's faster to do them on different modes...
- **Server owners**: Starting and ending zones are marked.

Source:
====================
